data.description: Large family, frequent overnight guests or just looking for room for a home office or gym? This home has it all with large bedrooms and two flex areas. Easy to maintain tile and luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the home. Downstairs there are two flex areas that can be a formal living room, formal dining, office, den, or game room. Family room/great room adjacent to the kitchen which has 2 pantries and a center island with sink and lots of storage. Enjoy bug free outdoor time in the screened lanai while admiring your open backyard. Upstairs you will find a loft, 3 bedrooms, guest bath and the master bedroom which features 2 walk in closets and Ensuite. Ensuite has a brand new tub surround. New roof in 2022, entire upper HVAC replaced and septic pumped in last two years make this home a perfect choice. Schedule your private visit today.
